sectionHeading: Regular traffic reports will resume Monday December 12 at 4:00 p.m.

incidentType: Traffic Advisory for New Circle Rd between Newtown Pike and Georgetown Rd:
location: Roadway shutdown in both directions until further notice due to downed pole and wires as a result of a collision.

incidentType: Traffic Advisory for New Circle Rd between Newtown Pike and Georgetown Rd:
location: Outer loop traffic diverted to Newtown Pike.  Inner loop traffic diverted to Georgetown Rd.

incidentType: Traffic Advisory for New Circle Rd between Newtown Pike and Georgetown Rd:
location: Significant delays also on Newtown Pike between I-75 and New Circle Rd.
